13. Redis Implementation Idea

    Using Redis atomic commands.
    
    INCR user123
    EXPIRE user123 60

    or Lua script.

14. Scaling Considerations
    1. Distributed nodes
    Multiple rate limiter servers.
    
    2. Consistency
    Use Redis atomic operations.
    
    3. Sharding
    Shard by:
    
    user_id % N
    4. Caching
    Hot users in memory.

15. Production Example

    APIs like:
    Google Cloud APIs
    Amazon Web Services
    Netflix microservices
    
